response.overview: Tři sestry: 30 (V Ještě Větší Aréně!) documents the Czech “pub-punk” favorites celebrating 30 years with their biggest arena show—recorded live on December 22, 2015 at O2 Arena in Prague. Featuring a full-length set packed with crowd singalongs and special guests, the concert is presented fully live (no playback or studio overdubs), capturing the band at peak energy in front of a sold-out arena.
response.tagline: 30 years. One massive arena. Fully live.
response.title: Tři Sestry: 30 (V Ještě Větší Aréně!)
